# kelly_stake_sizing.ts — Math Lockdown

Do NOT modify the mathematical formulas or logic in this file without a formal peer-review/approval step.

Protected:
- DEFAULT_BANKROLL_CONFIG (maxDailyRisk 0.10, sportWeights, structureWeights, minStake 5, maxStake 100).
- computeStake: effectiveKellyMultiplier, fullKellyStake, recommendedStake clamp, expectedProfit = stake*cardEv, risk thresholds (0.9, 0.5, 0.25) and riskLevel rules.
- computePortfolioAllocation: scalingFactor = maxDailyRisk/riskPercentage; drop if scaledStake < minStake.

Allowed without approval: comments. No changes to constants or formulas.
